{"tid":1023981,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【新巴刺針】81號巴士被插萬字夾女乘客中招","createTime":"2019-02-16T08:07:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T11:05:36.000Z","uid":17606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0001fc3552c454373067105a4a9581c38ea4b13d","tid":1023981,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:07:48.000Z","msg":"新巴巴士座椅被插針，一名乘客被刺傷。今（15日）上午約十時，一名女乘客乘搭新巴81號巴士時，疑被尾排左邊第二個座椅上的插針刺傷，遂通知車長和要求下車。車長隨即通知車務控制中心及報警求助，並將巴士停在英皇道1035號惠安苑對開，警察在車上檢獲一根兩厘米長的懷疑萬字夾碎片。該名乘客拒絕送院，自行離開。警員經初步調查，案件列求警調查，由東區警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。"},{"pid":"16956212f7da7c093add3532f0b05fdd53c5b528","tid":1023981,"uid":158145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:09:25.000Z","msg":"N賓？"},{"pid":"07aede22d5917677217f2d4bb2a44eef81f607be","tid":1023981,"uid":7940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:36:45.000Z","msg":"N賓住興華邨？"},{"pid":"7ae670a0004115d7963644f00f8093e5b808535e","tid":1023981,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T10:39:29.000Z","msg":"@nben"},{"pid":"25f7526698762dee47b994d45ab31eed78e043d2","tid":1023981,"uid":35351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T10:44:47.000Z","msg":"針灸治療<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789367e6121376d7a4ad393aba2682176ad604be","tid":1023981,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T11:05:36.000Z","msg":"做咩個個針對n賓？"}]}